  <statement>
    <p>
      Find the value of <m>t</m> for which <m>(x(t), y(t)) = (0,0)</m>. use
      the result of part (b) to  compute
      <m>\dfdx{y}{x}=\frac{\dot{y}}{\dot{x}}</m> at this time. Is
      this consistent with the graph?
</p>
</statement>
</task>
